    <item>
      <title>Version 1.0.5</title>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 May 2026 23:09:53 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>6</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.5</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Opt1 1.0.5 release notes</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
           font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; padding: 12px; }
    h1, h2, h3 { margin-top: 1em; }
    code { font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
           background: rgba(127,127,127,0.15); padding: 1px 4px;
           border-radius: 3px; }
    pre code { display: block; padding: 8px; }
    ul, ol { padding-left: 1.5em; }
    a { color: #0a84ff; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Opt1 1.0.5</h1>
<h2>What's new</h2>
<ul>
<li>Added the ability to add custom keybind instructions for all teleports.</li>
<li>Added the ability to mark a teleport item as not owned so it will not be suggested.</li>
<li>Debug mode is now on by default. You can opt out in settings.</li>
<li>Compass intersection now snaps to known dig spot if there is only one within range.</li>
<li>Improved scan guidance by adding pathing information to the scan optimiser (experimental).</li>
<li>Scan guidance UI (experimental) now shows teleport information if next spot is a teleport.</li>
<li>Opt1 is now open-source.</li>
</ul>
<h2>Fixes</h2>
<ul>
<li>Compass beams are no longer hidden when the map is zoomed in.</li>
<li>Fixed erroneous matches of 'treasure' in chat log text as clue scroll title</li>
<li>Fixed wilderness crater scan matching against deep wilderness scan</li>
<li>Added some missing teleports to dorgesh-kaan</li>
<li>Added validation of OCR'd scan range for scan clues to prevent inaccurate scan guidance</li>
</ul>
</body>
</html>
]]></description>
