    <item>
      <title>Version 1.0.3</title>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 13:38:41 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>4</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html lang="en"&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
  &lt;meta charset="UTF-8"&gt;
  &lt;title&gt;Opt1 1.0.3 release notes&lt;/title&gt;
  &lt;style&gt;
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
           font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; padding: 12px; }
    h1, h2, h3 { margin-top: 1em; }
    code { font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
           background: rgba(127,127,127,0.15); padding: 1px 4px;
           border-radius: 3px; }
    pre code { display: block; padding: 8px; }
    ul, ol { padding-left: 1.5em; }
    a { color: #0a84ff; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  &lt;/style&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;Opt1 1.0.3&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What's new&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Significantly improved Celtic Knot detection and solving.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Celtic knot no longer requires inversion for every puzzle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Added an additional set of auto-triangulation points for Arc compasses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fixed lockbox and towers puzzles not detecting on larger screens.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experimental support for RS3 in game UI scaling (tell us your scale in settings!).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The map in the compass window now zooms in on any calculated intersection.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Signficantly improved Scan clue detection.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experimental support for scan clue pathing guidance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your choice to 'show all spots' in the compass window is now remembered.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fixed some teleport locations showing in the wrong place.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dig spots and teleport locations now show on the Arc map.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;General improvements to matching of clue text.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compass window is now moveable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scan window is now resizeable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Aligned themeing across all windows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Release notes should now display properly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
</description>
